ወዘአዕለዋ፡ ለዛቲ፡ መጽሐፍ። ይቤ፡ ሕፁፅ፡ ወኃጥእ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis" resp="PRS10171Wright"/>ወዘአጽሐፈኒ፡ ፍሥሓ፡ ክርስቶስ። ነዳየ፡
አእምሮ፡ ወምስነ፡ ጥበብ፡
<note>The colophon states that the manuscript was written for <persName ref="PRS11074Fesseha">Fǝśśǝḥa Krǝstos</persName> in the seventh year of
